  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Podiatrist",
  "description": "<p><strong>👣 Senior Podiatrist Wanted – Join Our Growing Team! 👣</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Heartland Rehab is expanding, and we’re looking for a <strong>Senior Podiatrist</strong> to join our dynamic team! If you’re passionate about <strong>helping people move pain-free</strong>, thrive in a <strong>collaborative healthcare setting</strong>, and want to be part of a <strong>progressive, patient-focused clinic</strong>, we’d love to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 About the Role:</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Diagnose and treat a wide range of foot and lower limb conditions</p>\n<p>✅ Provide <strong>evidence-based podiatric care</strong> for sports injuries, diabetic foot management, and biomechanics</p>\n<p>✅ Work alongside <strong>physiotherapists and healthcare professionals</strong> for a holistic approach to patient care</p>\n<p>✅ Enjoy <strong>flexible hours, a competitive base salary, and commission incentives</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ <strong>Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Podiatry</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ <strong>At least 5 years of clinical experience</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ Strong clinical expertise in lower limb conditions and gait analysis</p>\n<p>✔️ Outgoing, team-oriented, and patient-focused</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>💰 <strong>Competitive base salary + commission incentives</strong></p>\n<p>⏳ <strong>Flexible working hours to suit your lifestyle</strong></p>\n<p>📚 <strong>Training funds</strong> to support continuous professional development</p>\n<p>🏥 <strong>Modern, fully-equipped clinics</strong> with the latest technology</p>\n<p>📈 <strong>Career growth opportunities</strong> in a thriving healthcare environment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join a team that values <strong>trust, teamwork, and excellence in patient care</strong>. If you’re ready to take the next step in your career, apply now!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📩 Send your CV to <strong>jobs@heartlandrehab.sg</strong> – we look forward to meeting you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>#Podiatrist #HealthcareJobs #FootHealth #CareerGrowth #JoinOurTeam</p>",
